Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths, and career counselors assist unsure students by redirecting them toward applicable industries. Nearby, alumni volunteers gather at the coffee station to provide quick pep talks, fostering supportive interactions among attendees. Before the event opens, students line up outside the gym, excited to explore the available opportunities. Inside, they engage in lively interactions, comparing swag items like water bottles and phone chargers, while some rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, contributing to the energetic environment.

Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths, and career counselors assist unsure students by redirecting them toward applicable industries. Nearby, alumni volunteers gather at the coffee station to provide quick pep talks, fostering supportive interactions among attendees. Before the event opens, students line up outside the gym, excited to explore available opportunities. Inside, they engage in lively interactions, comparing swag items like water bottles and phone chargers, while some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, contributing to the energetic environment of the event.
